Each monthly season, we'll be introducing 4 new Battle Units that you can earn by ranking up on the Season Ranked Ladder. Based on your highest rank achieved during the season, you can earn:

RANK 20 REWARD
1 x Monthly Epic + Spirit + Gold

RANK 10 REWARD
1 x Monthly Legendary + 1 x Monthly Epic + Spirit + Gold

RANK 5 REWARD
1 x Monthly Rare + 1 x Monthly Legendary + 1 x Monthly Epic + Spirit + Gold

RANK: S-Rank REWARD
1 x Monthly Common + 1 x RANDOM Legendary + 1 x Monthly Rare + 1 x Monthly Legendary + 1 x Monthly Epic + Spirit + Gold